# Testing (DailyDiffs)

- **Write comprehensive tests** for all non-trivial logic: tap/difference detection, scoring, streak logic, username validation, API routes.
- **Test the UI**: include component tests and, where useful, integration tests for critical flows (e.g. play screen, login wall).
- Prefer testing behavior and outcomes; avoid testing implementation details.
- Keep tests fast and deterministic; mock Supabase and external APIs in unit/integration tests.
- When adding a feature, add or update tests in the same change; do not leave tests for "later."
